40
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:10,458
No. Not that I’m aware of, anyway.

41
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:13,916
Only on Saturday,
when he lashed out at Mr. Doppler.

42
00:09:15,666 --> 00:09:17,583
As if your father-in-law
