48
00:10:42,583 --> 00:10:44,500
DO NOT OPEN BEFORE NOVEMBER 4, 10:13 P.M.

49
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,208
- That’s impossible.
- What?

50
00:10:54,166 --> 00:10:55,416
